tasks.task:
Write test: MLflow run discovery finds all Layer C analysis/ensemble runs.
Test that discover_source_runs() finds runs in minivess_evaluation with: - ensemble_strategy tag (per_loss_single_best, etc.) - Inherited model_family (or "ensemble" for multi-model ensembles) - Per-volume metrics at: eval/{fold_id}/vol/{volume_id}/{metric}
For debug: 96 post-training x 4 ensemble strategies = 384 evaluation runs. For production: 432 post-training x 5 ensemble strategies = 2160 evaluation runs.

Write test: factorial config auto-parsing from composable YAML.
Parse configs/factorial/debug.yaml -> extract factors dict with 3 sections:
  factors.training -> {model_family: [...], loss_name: [...], aux_calibration: [...]}
  factors.post_training -> {method: [...], recalibration: [...]}
  factors.analysis -> {ensemble_strategy: [...]}
Verify the total product = 384 (debug) or 720 (paper_full).
Verify that factor names are AUTO-DERIVED from YAML keys, not hardcoded.
Also verify: a hypothetical my_lab.yaml with 2x1x1x1x1x2 = 4 conditions works.
